			(property "Description" "ADS1015 - 12-bit 4-Channel I2C ADC with Internal PGA\n\n• VDD: 2.0-5.5V\n• Sampling Rate: 3.3ksps\n• Gain Settings: 2/3, 1, 2, 4, 8, 16\n• I2C Address: ADDR low = 1001000x, ADDR high = 1001001x\n\nInternal Comparator\n\nThe ADS1015 includes an internal comparator that can be set to output a high-level on ALERT when the conversion results exceeeds a pre-defined upper level, and will deassert itself when the level falls below a pre-defined lower threshold level. It can also be set to windowed mode where the ALERT pin will be asserted if the data exceeds the upper threshold or falls below the lower threshold."
				(at 0 0 0)
				(effects
					(font
						(size 1.27 1.27)
					)
					(hide yes)
				)
			)
